Despite the busyness of 2023, it concluded with some amazing memories. I am grateful to all the couples and their families who allowed me to be a part of their wedding festivities. Not only did I have the chance to adorn some incredible individuals with henna, but I also had a delightful time doing so. It warms my heart when clients become friends and even family, and last year I was fortunate to experience a lot of that. I am eagerly waiting to meet my 2024 brides. Hope this year is going to be as amazing as last year.
